works.description:
I recently found out my photo is being  
used throughout this Android
application. Well actually it was my friend who found it and she told me  

about it. I feel really uncomfortable having my photo displayed
everywhere... This photo was really only meant to be viewed by my friends,
 
but for some reason the developer is using it in this application. Since I
 
took this photo and because it's a photo of myself, I believe it's  
copyrighted by me.
